Validating advanced xml - GenerateStringfromResource(String path)
read all the xml as bytes and return as string.

Serialization and Deserialization using POJO classes
Request and Response spec builders

Cucumber, Gherkin syntax, StepDefinition, Feature file, Tidygherkin plugin, Test Runner.
